# Hi, I'm Abhishek PR

Entry-level DevOps and Cloud learner building hands-on projects with Linux, Docker, Terraform, AWS, GitHub Actions, CI/CD, and monitoring.

## What I've Built

### Terraform AWS Production Lab
Built an AWS infrastructure lab using Terraform with VPC, subnet, internet gateway, route table, security group, EC2, S3 remote state, state locking, modules, drift detection, and import workflow.

### Calculator CI/CD Pipeline
Built a Flask API with Pytest, GitHub Actions, SonarCloud, Docker, DockerHub, and AWS EC2 deployment.

### Docker Multi-App
Built a multi-container Docker project using Flask, Nginx reverse proxy, and Docker networking.

### Kingdom Frontier 2D
Built and deployed a browser-based 2D game using React, Vite, Phaser, JavaScript, and CSS.

## Current Focus

- AWS SAA-C03 preparation
- Terraform Infrastructure as Code
- Docker and container networking
- CI/CD with GitHub Actions
- Linux troubleshooting
- Monitoring and alerting

## Goal

To become job-ready for entry-level DevOps and Cloud Engineer roles by building practical projects and documenting them clearly.
